title: Lloyd's insurer Apollo to stop underwriting Adani coal mine from Sept. 2021 - Reuters India
description: Lloyd's of London firm Apollo has written insurance for Adani Enterprises' <ADEL.NS> Carmichael thermal coal mine which expires in Sept 2021 but is not planning to provide any further insurance for the mine, according to a memo seen by Reuters.
